es+of+a+Black+Priesthood+Holder&amp;rft.pub=Cedar+Fort&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-4621-0356-0&amp;rft.au=W.+Kesler+Jackson&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D4EwCdjQ7uvoC&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+people+and+temple+and+priesthood+policies+in+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
