<li id="cite_note-94"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-94">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFWatt1880" class="citation book cs1">Watt, G. D. (1880). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/digital/collection/JournalOfDiscourses3/id/2862">"Intelligence, Etc."</a>. In Young, Brigham (ed.). <i><a href="/wiki/Journal_of_Discourses" title="Journal of Discourses">Journal of Discourses</a></i>. Vol.&#160;7. Liverpool: Amasa Lyman. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-60096-015-4" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-60096-015-4"><bdi>978-1-60096-015-4</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young_University" title="Brigham Young University">Brigham Young University</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Intelligence%2C+Etc.&amp;rft.btitle=Journal+of+Discourses&amp;rft.place=Liverpool&amp;rft.pub=Amasa+Lyman&amp;rft.date=1880&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-60096-015-4&amp;rft.aulast=Watt&amp;rft.aufirst=G.+D.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fcontentdm.lib.byu.edu%2Fdigital%2Fcollection%2FJournalOfDiscourses3%2Fid%2F2862&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+people+and+temple+and+priesthood+policies+in+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
