<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBush1973" class="citation cs2">Bush, Lester E. Jr. (Spring 1973), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.dialoguejournal.com/wp-content/uploads/sbi/articles/Dialogue_V08N01_13.pdf">"Mormonism's Negro Doctrine: An Historical Overview"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>, <i><a href="/wiki/Dialogue:_A_Journal_of_Mormon_Thought" title="Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought">Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought</a></i>, <b>8</b> (1): 11–68, <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F45227533">10.2307/45227533</a>, <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/45227533">45227533</a><span class="reference-accessdate">, retrieved <span class="nowrap">November 1,</span> 2012</span></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Dialogue%3A+A+Journal+of+Mormon+Thought&amp;rft.atitle=Mormonism%27s+Negro+Doctrine%3A+An+Historical+Overview&amp;rft.ssn=spring&amp;rft.volume=8&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=11-68&amp;rft.date=1973&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F45227533&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F45227533%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft.aulast=Bush&amp;rft.aufirst=Lester+E.+Jr.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dialoguejournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsbi%2Farticles%2FDialogue_V08N01_13.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+people+and+temple+and+priesthood+policies+in+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></li>
